$ Dataverse: table

Tables can be creted in → Microsoft/products/Power/Apps: navigation pane -> Data -> Tables -> New Table.

{ Standard tables

  Dataverse comes with a set of (undeletable but hidable) *standard table* that model core business requirements.

  A table can be linked to other tables with one-to-many or many-to-many relationship

}

{ Activity tables

  Default activity tables include:
    • Appointment
    • Recurring Appointment
    • Task
    • Email
    • Fax
    • Letter
    • Phone Call

}

{ Ownership

  A table is either
    • *User or team owned*, or
    • *Organization owned*

  After creating a table, ownership cannot be changed.

  An activity table cannot be organization owned.

}

